<plot>During the Israeli-Lebanese war, five Israeli soldiers were sent to Lebanon to set a three-day ambush against terrorist units who were trying to cross the border into Israel. The three days of sleepless nights, canned food, minimal hygiene and silence seemed endless. The last day of the ambush was my last day in Lebanon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384280</url></doc>
